NAME

DateTime::Locale::dyo - Locale data examples for the Jola-Fonyi (dyo) locale

DESCRIPTION

This pod file contains examples of the locale data available for the Jola-Fonyi locale.

Date Formats

Full

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = Talata 5 Fébirie 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = Arjuma 22 Disambar 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = Sibiti 15 Settembar -10

Long

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 5 Fébirie 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22 Disambar 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15 Settembar -10

Medium

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 5 Fe 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22 De 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15 Se -10

Short

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 5/2/2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22/12/1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15/9/-10

Available Formats

Bh (h B)

   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 9 B
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 4 B
